989-### Functional Requirements
990-
991-| Req ID | Requirement |
992-|---|---|
993:| M06-FR-001 | System shall create documentation checklist automatically after sanction. |
994:| M06-FR-002 | System shall assign document preparation to Compliance Team. |
995:| M06-FR-003 | System shall collect witness PAN and Aadhaar. |
996:| M06-FR-004 | System shall validate witness as existing SFPCL shareholder. |
997:| M06-FR-005 | System shall require cancelled cheque for bank verification. |
998:| M06-FR-006 | System shall require blank-dated cheque as security and capture custody details. |
999:| M06-FR-007 | System shall generate / track Power of Attorney in favour of Company Secretary. |
1000:| M06-FR-008 | System shall require ₹500 stamp and notarisation for PoA. |
1001:| M06-FR-009 | System shall generate / track Tri-party Agreement where subsidiary repayment is applicable. |
1002:| M06-FR-010 | System shall generate / track SH-4 for physical shares. |
1003:| M06-FR-011 | System shall track CDSL pledge for demat shares. |
1004:| M06-FR-012 | System shall track future-share pledge obligation. |
1005:| M06-FR-013 | System shall generate Term Sheet with mandatory terms. |
1006:| M06-FR-014 | System shall enforce Term Sheet signature routing based on loan amount. |
1007:| M06-FR-015 | System shall generate Loan Agreement and require ₹500 stamp and notarisation. |
1008:| M06-FR-016 | System shall detect / allow flagging of signature mismatch. |
1009:| M06-FR-017 | System shall generate Bank Verification Letter or require borrower declaration for signature mismatch. |
1010:| M06-FR-018 | System shall maintain final checklist index. |
1011:| M06-FR-019 | System shall block disbursement until checklist is complete and approved. |
