+# Review Range and Diagnostics
+
+## Pinned range
+
+- Fixed point: `329c3b03e5e25535e84f7469899cac063e5e9404`
+- Reviewed head: `092faf7a`
+- Diff: `git diff 329c3b03...092faf7a`
